 \"the three-pointer\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"the USA\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike football, basketball or cricket players, track and field athletes rarely get the opportunity to showcase their skills to the world, making the pressure to perform at the quadrennial Olympics the ultimate pressure cooker.\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"football, basketball or cricket players\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"track and field athletes\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"their skills\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2696}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"the quadrennial Olympics\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"the ultimate pressure cooker\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This wonderful photo of the USA's Gabrielle Thomas crossing the finish line in the 200m (219-yard) sprint final encapsulates the huge relief athletes feel upon reaching their lifelong dream of a gold medal.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9998501786424577, \"rank\": 0.00014620346263985017, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2822, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabrielle Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/r